reviewText: Crazy, zany, terrible drive-in b-movie madness. What's not to love!
Don't waste your time. Stupid and stupider can't describe how stupid this move is.

I gave this one star because this movie is already on amazon, and is available for free with your Prime membership. This version is someone trying to cash in on old campy sci fi movies.

If you already have Prime, save your money, search "Invsion of the Bee Girls" and enjoy this movie without spending a dime
